# Synapse Core: Workspace Protocol

## Architectural Constraints
- This is a PLUGIN-BASED system. 
- Core logic resides in `/core`. 
- Generated features MUST reside in `/skills`.
- Every skill MUST inherit from `core.base_skill.BaseSkill`.

## Security & Safety
- DO NOT execute generated code on the host machine.
- ALWAYS use the `core.sandbox.SandboxManager` for verification (to be built in Phase 2).

## Formatting
- Use Type Hints for everything.
- Maintain a strictly modular directory structure.